---
title: Summer Lamb Shortloin & Roast Veggie Salad for Dinner with Chocolate Brownies & Strawberry Compote for Dessert
description: Sear a tender and succulent lamb loin that's just right for a gourmet-style dinner. With all the flavour of traditional roast lamb, plus wholesome veggies, it's sure to have you feeling satisfied with every delicious mouthful. And the best meals end with a sweet treat, so we've included a serving of chocolate brownies with a strawberry compote for dessert!
